{"tid":524092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為進軍美國受挫，傳 AT&T 放棄合作計劃","createTime":"2018-01-09T08:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T19:10:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3abfb34cfd3d049ee1027b349ea0d776968e780","tid":524092,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"2018 年是 HUAWEI 華為大舉進軍美國的一年，華為原本更打算在 CES 發佈會上，正式宣佈跟美國第二大網絡商 AT&amp;T 達成合作協議，並正式推出旗艦機 Mate 10 Pro。<br />\n<br />\n不過據華爾街日報報導，AT&amp;T 現時決定放棄跟華為合作，而華為則繼續透過網上商店及線下實體店銷售解鎖版電話。<br />\n<br />\n雖然進軍美國市場的計劃暫時受挫，但華為現時仍然是全球第三大智能機廠商，僅次於 Samsung 及 Apple，而華為也目標在兩年內成為第二大智能機品牌，並於五年內登上第一位。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n來源：華爾街日報"},{"pid":"78c0e3b0e00b42561e15a692ced7fce14b0434d2","tid":524092,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ringhk.com/news2.php?id=16244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fringhk.com%2Fnews2.php%3Fid%3D16244&d=U%2BkWzTdhjVf0XVIsnGw%2Bv9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b096f5d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ringhk.com/news2.php?id=16244</a>"},{"pid":"8823cd9b4319c0ef1bcde0fad84326f425f9fd21","tid":524092,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913cb662a27628c8da66cff6975b79d839fc9ced","tid":524092,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:50:59.000Z","msg":"聽過名都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b214564829b1d93a801e887e4f7573c4e6e62025","tid":524092,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:19:02.000Z","msg":"撚狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb980e292fd076b7287e44a83b2a268686f5dfd","tid":524092,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:23:19.000Z","msg":"華為係美國無運行啦<br />\